author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Humanwell Healthcare's 2017 Net Profit Up, Plans Debt Financing Instruments And Commercial Paper
text:
April 11 (Reuters) - Humanwell Healthcare Group Co Ltd :
* SAYS 2017 NET PROFIT UP 148.5 PERCENT Y/Y AT 2.1 BILLION YUAN ($334.18 million)
* SAYS IT PLANS TO ISSUE UP TO 2.0 BILLION YUAN DEBT FINANCING INSTRUMENTS, 4.0 BILLION YUAN COMMERCIAL PAPER Source text in Chinese: bit.ly/2GSYme1 ； bit.ly/2v9F7LQ ； bit.ly/2HsDk6W Further company coverage: ($1 = 6.2841 Chinese yuan renminbi) (Reporting by Hong Kong newsroom)
